lyrics.text: Our best friends befriend good ones.
you are hair's thickness and lights [ you're acting big while you're nothing and all you care about is spotlights]
coyotes with retail prices [ coyotes eat dead meat after lions, so he is describing mohamed ramadan as a cheap coyote who steals after the lion(Wegz)]
If you're daddy so who am I [ Cause both mohamed ramadan and wegz had tracks called I'm daddy]
we're not the same color we're not equal [  color  here means music genre, as mohamed ramadan is just selling commercial songs, not any art]
you raw meat that can't be cooked
my chest is wide I could contain u [ like mothers contain their kids when they are angry and crying]
business is business and I know how I could get even with you
an eye for an eye and all what it takes is a bullet
your face is a pedal i step on and you're engine produces weird voices
All the action you are involved in is only TV stunt, not real.
A tribute to where is wegz from and what music genre he is playing
I am younger but I can really go wild on you
oh My gazelle ( a weapon's name in egypt) can hunt you you drunk prey

my armoy is smary, yours is dumb af
my gazelle is my top I could 700 on my own
without training, I am number one [ Mohamed Ramadan had a soundtrack that he is number one]
tribute to where he is from

You steal from everyone while I shoot live ammunition
I have solid roots and I care about them
all you care about is immature children.
I bury it in his face, I put out my cigarettes in his eyes. I am full I don't need to steal like you, my intensions are all good.
I am all satisfied not greedy as you
They are blinded by greed and they feel their time is gone
you show off your muscles but don't act tough
you just get mad not rage
